data.value: Uh oh. We made an oopsie! D: This is known as a bug, and it means that Power Patcher is seconds away from crashing, held back only by this almighty dialog. Don't worry. It's (probably) nothing you did. There's also nothing you CAN do, besides try again. If that doesn't work, and you still see this lovely box, PLEASE report the error! To assist you in this, we've prepared a highly technical report, which is presented below. If you submit that report, along with as much information about what you were doing, our team of highly trained sea-monkeys will get to work on fixing it for you.
